							<h6 class="proxima-nova-bold uppercase" style="color: #fb4b4b;">Option 1</h6>
							<p style="color: #292929;">Layered structure – tap and swipe interaction. <br>Both navigation levels are accessible at any time.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="column--s-12">
