							<p style="color: #292929;">Vertical structure – tap interaction, displayed via collapse animation. <br>Clear division between topics.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="column--s-12">
						<img src="./assets/img/content/redbull/02-redbull.jpg" class="responsive" alt="">
